## §A.3 Cycle history

- **cycle 1 (2026-05-06)**: v1.0.0 RELEASED — rtsc + sc 시드, 3-link
  substrate-of-substrates 도식 wired.
- **cycle 2 (2026-05-07 ~ 2026-05-08)**: v1.1.0 RSC code-layer FINAL —
  iter 1 ~ 19, recipe `~/core/bedrock/docs/runnable_surface_recipe.md`
  적용. T1 ×6 (lattice + cross-doc + 4 calc) + T2 ×9 (4 numerics + 4
  parity + lattice_arithmetic) + T2-solver ×4 (BCS / McMillan / Hc2 /
  LK-99 Newton inversions) + T3-archival ×6 (arXiv 6-corpus 존재 검증)
  + meta ×2 (falsifier_check + lint_numerics). 모든 6 falsifier
  100% bookkeeping closure. recipe §7.2 sat-1 + sat-2 통과 후 user
  override 로 §7.7 (a) 예외 발동, archival T3 추가.
- **cycle 2-post (2026-05-08 심화 봉쇄)**: 사용자 명시 지시
  ("심화 봉쇄 진행", recipe §9.1 합법 예외 #2) 로 recipe §7.4 우선순위
  표 미충족 슬롯 2 개를 충족.
    - **iter #1**: 슬롯 #15 (`saturation_check.hexa`). meta tier
      ×2 → ×3. 22-check predicate (sat-1 ×6 + sat-2 ×2 + drift-lock
      ×1 + falsifier mirror) 가 `__HEXA_RTSC_RSC_SATURATED__ STOP`
      sentinel 을 자동 emit.
    - **iter #2**: 슬롯 #7 (`numerics_cross_pillar.hexa`). T2
      cross-cutter ×1 → ×2 (lattice_arithmetic + cross_pillar).
      6 inter-pillar invariants (I1 SSOT lattice presence, I2 master
      identity, I3 Hc2 σ·τ=48 gate, I4 Cooper φ=2, I5 McMillan→BCS
      weak-coupling limit, I6 LK-99 negative-result σ-preservation).
      drift-lock between 4 pillar bodies — silent pillar-level
      corruption catches.
    - **iter #3**: 슬롯 #11 (`tests/test_saturation.hexa`). isolated
      regression test for `verify/saturation_check.hexa` (sentinel
      ends in STOP not PASS, so test_calculators 가 미커버). 4 조건
      (count 9/9 + sat-1 TRUE + sat-2 TRUE + STOP sentinel) AND
      iter #1 prose 의 "22-check" → "9-check" 정정 wave.
    - **iter #4**: 슬롯 #12 (`build/Makefile` + `build/header.tex`).
      pandoc + xelatex 3-corpus PDF rebuild (pillars + roadmap +
      hardware). Non-predicate-bearing reader-facing tool — closure
      pct 변동 없음.
    - **iter #5**: 슬롯 #13 (`docs/numerics_methodology.md`).
      T1/T2/T3/T4 4-tier 사다리 narrative + 4 pillar 방법론 prose +
      "What's NOT covered" honesty disclaimer + "How to add a new
      pillar" 7-step gateway. Non-predicate-bearing.
  closure-honesty: 여전히 bookkeeping/archival 만, T4 live hardware
  는 §A.6 Step 4 미해결. recipe §7.4 priority table 모든 슬롯
  (#1-#15 + cross-cutters) 충족 → §9.1 saturation 후 health-check
  모드만 가능 (3가지 합법 예외 외 새 chunk 금지).

